info.prompt: ### Give a funny scenario for Actually, this is my first rodeo. completion:
info.completion: A man in a cowboy outfit is standing in the middle of an office. Everyone is looking at him curiously.A man dressed as a cowboy walks into an office and everyone stops to stare.The CEO of an office walks into work wearing a full cowgirl outfit, complete with hat and boots. Everyone stares in disbelief.
